title: Windows 10 Manager 1.0.3 + Patch
description:
Windows 10 Manager is a system utility that helps you optimize, tweak, repair and clean up Windows 10. It will increase your system speed, eliminate system fault, improve system security, and meet all of your expectations. 


Changes in v1.0.3:

- Add and perfect some tweaks in Custom System. 
- Perfect some features. 
- Perfect the feature that optimize services. 
- Fix the bug in Lock System. 
- Fix the bug that cannot restart in Registry Defrag
